[b]This thread is dedicated to tracking bugs and implementing community-sourced fixes. To ensure the mod remains high-quality and avoids redundant work, please follow the guidelines below when reporting an issue.[/b]
[h3]📝 Reporting Guidelines[/h3]
To help identify and resolve issues quickly, and spare us time, please provide as much detail as possible. We highly encourage including:
[list]
[*][b]Links to Official Bug Reports[/b]: If the bug has been documented on the Paradox Forums.
[*][b]Known Fixes[/b]: If you have already identified the specific code or script file that resolves the issue.
[*][b]Reproduction Steps[/b]: How to make the bug happen in a clean environment.
[/list]
[i]Thank you for helping keep Stellaris polished and playable![/i]
